Nic Newling struggled with undiagnosed bipolar disorder between the ages of 13 and 18  . 
  He was diagnosed with the condition after his older brother Christopher killed himself . 
  The 28-year-old is now a mental health advocate to raise awareness of mental illness . 
  He struggled through the confusing highs and deep depressions of his disorder . 
  He was finally diagnosed with bipolar disorder when he was 18 . 
  His brother Christopher was also diagnosed with mental illnesses . 
  Nic Newling is now using his story to help others with mental health issues . 
 